records.name: Adaaran Select Huduran Fushi - Free Dine Around Premium All Inclusive 24 Hours - 1 Child Stays Free Between April 2025 To September 2025 - 45 Mins By Speedboat

descriptions.direction: Located in Lhohifushi, Adaaran Select Huduran Fushi - with 24hrs Premium All Inclusive is on a private beach. Sultans Surf Spot and Honky's Surf Spot are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Paradise Island Beach and Gili Lankanfushi Beach. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as windsurfing.
descriptions.general: Adaaran Select Hudhuran Fushi is an island paradise with one of the best left-hand surf break points in the world. With 24-hour access by speedboat, it is nestled on one of the oldest natural islands in the Maldives and offers 24-hour premium, all-inclusive for surfers, honeymooners, families, and groups seeking an unforgettable tropical vacation experience. Fully air-conditioned, the private beach and over-water villas come with a cable/satellite TV and minibar. En-suite bathrooms have an outdoor rain shower and a hairdryer. Adaaran Select Huduran Fushi - Premium All Inclusive is about 19 km from Male International Airport. From there, it is 30 minutes by speedboat to the island. Chavana Spa features a relaxing menu of massage therapies, spa baths, and facials. Guests may also make use of the on-site water sports facilities to kite surf, dive, and board. A gym is also available. International buffet spreads are served at Banyan Restaurant & the Indian Pavilion Lhohis Wave, while the outdoor Sunset Restaurant offers candlelight seafood dinners and wine. Cocktails can be enjoyed at Lohis Bar and Hiyala Bar. Enjoy daily complimentary snorkeling trips for every booking. For a truly immersive Maldivian adventure, reserve 5 nights and receive one free excursion, or extend your stay to over 6 nights and enjoy two free excursions. Honeymooners' benefits: Romantic Bed decoration - once per stay. One Honeymoon cake
